""SELECT `p`.`KeyId`, `p`.`Author`, `p`.`BookCategoryFK`, `p`.`BookTitle`, `p`.`DateCreated`, `p`.`DateModified`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`Height`, `p`.`Img`, `p`.`Length`, `p`.`MerchantFK`, `p`.`PageNumber`, `p`.`Quantity`, `p`.`Rating`, `p`.`RatingNumber`, `p`.`Status`, `p`.`UnitPrice`, `p`.`Width`, `p`.`isPaperback`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`KeyId`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`Address`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`Bank`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`BankAccountNotificationLinkImg`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`BankBranch`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`BussinessRegisterId`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`BussinessRegisterLinkImg`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`ContactAddress`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`DateCreated`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`DateModified`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`DirectContactName`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`EstablishDate`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`Hotline`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`LegalRepresentative`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`MerchantBankingName`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`MerchantCompanyName`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`Scales`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`Status`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`TaxId`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`TaxRegisterLinkImg`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`UserFK`, `p.MerchantFKNavigation`.`Website`, `p.BookCategoryFKNavigation`.`KeyId`, `p.BookCategoryFKNavigation`.`BookCategoryName`, `p.BookCategoryFKNavigation`.`Status`
FROM `Books` AS `p`
